raise your voice to me!

01:10:51.126 --> 01:10:53.128
Do you know who you're talkin' to?

01:10:53.295 --> 01:10:56.423
I happen to be Buford T. Justice,

01:10:56.590 --> 01:11:00.427
a distinguished officer
of over 30 years' seniority!

01:11:00.594 --> 01:11:03.972
One of the most highly respected
law-enforcement agents...

01:11:04.139 --> 01:11:07.559
in the United States of America.

01:11:07.726 --> 01:11:12.815
That vehicle happens to be
evidence, valuable evidence,

01:11:12.981 --> 01:11:18.278
that's going to convict a maniac
that I've been tryin' to apprehend

01:11:18.445 --> 01:11:22.491
and that I have been
in high-speed pursuit of

01:11:22.658 --> 01:11:24.743
for 700 miles.

01:11:26.662 --> 01:11:30.833
He is wanted for the Mann Act,
kidnappin'

01:11:30.999 --> 01:11:36.213
and the attempted murder
of over 20 brother officers.

01:11:41.927 --> 01:11:46.807
Sir, I'm sorry. I had no idea.

01:11:47.933 --> 01:11:53.230
It never occurred to me... Well, please, sir,
you proceed immediately, and...

01:11:53.397 --> 01:11:56.150
I hope you'll accept my apologies
for my profanity.

01:11:57.484 --> 01:12:03.365
Apology accepted.
Now...

01:12:11.415 --> 01:12:14.626
How about you, Bandit?
You copy this Snowman? Come on.

01:12:14.793 --> 01:12:16.920
I got ya, son. Come on back.

01:12:17.087 --> 01:12:21.592
You ain't gonna believe this,
