Actually, my heaviest relationship
was with an acid-rock singer...

01:12:58.670 --> 01:13:00.339
named Robert Crumly.

01:13:00.506 --> 01:13:06.178
We were together... eight and a half days.
God, I really thought that was it.

01:13:06.345 --> 01:13:07.805
And?

01:13:07.971 --> 01:13:11.266
One day I came home
and found him in the shower...

01:13:11.433 --> 01:13:14.353
...with a girl...
and her mother!

01:13:14.520 --> 01:13:18.190
Well, at least
he kept it in the family.

01:13:26.114 --> 01:13:28.992
You have a wonderful way
of putting things.

01:13:29.159 --> 01:13:32.246
- So did he.
- Oh, yes.

01:13:36.458 --> 01:13:39.711
<i>Breaker one-nine.
This is the Bandit.</i>

01:13:39.878 --> 01:13:43.173
<i>I'm lookin' for a west-bounder
on highway 85.</i>

01:13:43.340 --> 01:13:45.634
<i>I need a smokey report,
and I need it bad, son.</i>

01:13:45.801 --> 01:13:49.680
This is Foxy Lady, Bandit.
We heard you were comin' by,

01:13:49.847 --> 01:13:52.558
and we decided we'd take care
of those bears for you.

01:13:52.724 --> 01:13:57.813
- You know, a little "personalised service".
- Send me the bill, Foxy Lady.

01:13:57.980 --> 01:14:01.316
Better yet, why don't you
come by and pay up in person?

01:14:02.276 --> 01:14:06.446
