01:14:06.613 --> 01:14:08.323
- Daddy, listen.
- Shut up!

01:14:08.490 --> 01:14:10.492
<i>But I'm just ahead of you.</i>

01:14:10.701 --> 01:14:13.495
I'm at mile marker 86.
Come on by, Bandit.

01:14:13.662 --> 01:14:15.664
