01:17:52.214 --> 01:17:54.842
Thank you, Mr B.
I don't know how to thank ya.

01:17:55.008 --> 01:17:57.636
You can thank me
by not gettin' caught.

01:17:57.803 --> 01:18:00.806
Have a good day and a better one
tomorrow, good buddy.

01:18:00.973 --> 01:18:03.809
Hey, Bandit,
this is Little Beaver.

01:18:03.976 --> 01:18:07.771
Put your foot on the floor.
We got your back door, and I'm clear.

01:18:07.938 --> 01:18:12.234
That's a 10-4.
Snowman, you got your ears on, son?

01:18:13.443 --> 01:18:15.571
You've got him, you lucky devil.

01:18:15.737 --> 01:18:17.656
<i>You're about to come up on a convoy.</i>

01:18:17.823 --> 01:18:20.492
Keep your rubber band
stretched real tight.

01:18:20.659 --> 01:18:25.289
10-4, 10-4.
I'm bringin' it, son. I'm clear.

