dressed like me. You can't miss me.

01:33:29.026 --> 01:33:31.111
<i>10-4.</i>

01:33:33.864 --> 01:33:36.408
Wait a minute.
Scratch that. Hold it.

01:33:36.575 --> 01:33:41.163
I can't lie to you, Sheriff. You're too good
